---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Curly Sheep";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="homepage">
    <div class="gif">
        <img src="/images/space.webp" role="presentation" width="300" height="259" decoding="async" class="mx-auto">
    </div>
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
    <span class="badge">The Mighty Herbivore</span>
    <h2 class="my-[20px]">About</h2>
    <p>
        羊星居羊卷卷。喜欢嘟囔一些日常小事，很少进行大思考。
    </p>
    <p>可以在<a href="https://moresci.sale/@bipolar" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">长毛象</a>捕捉到卷毛羊的更多生活动态！</p>
    <h2 class="my-[20px]">Interests</h2>
    <p>
        爱好基本都很安静，翻翻闲书插插花喝喝茶什么的。
    </p>
    <p>偶尔遇到能让自己上头的游戏或者小说，也会不分昼夜地玩。</p>
    <p>还特别热衷于装饰自己的羊圈，三天两头就会炫耀自己的家（…）</p>
    <p>自我观察是羊生课题。</p>
    <h2 class="my-[20px]">Friends</h2>
    <p>
        欢迎跟羊交换友情链接！（扭动）
    </p>
    <ul class="pl-8 list-disc">
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://naturaleki.one/" title="Across the street, cross one’s heart." target="_blank">天堂错误文件</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://ocod.netlify.app/" target="_blank" title="">稽异录残篇</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://ccaatthouse.icu" title="我们不生产猫头气球" target="_blank">猫头气球生产工厂</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://luoshui.icu/" title="小心！野兽凶猛！" target="_blank">此地有野狗出没</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://notion-next-neon-eight.vercel.app/" title="" target="_blank">Mimoshark’s Blog</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://wbzddwsw.vercel.app/" title="不作诗则做诗" target="_blank">树响集</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://blog-sooty-beta.vercel.app/" title="记生活迷思，做吟游诗人" target="_blank">漫游者迷路中</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://hirate3.wordpress.com/" title="欢迎访问虚拟仓库" target="_blank">AI碎片缓存</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://summerwasover.vercel.app/" title="像鸟儿编辑它们的飞行一般书写" target="_blank">晴空</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://xyzxy.me" title="桂棹兮兰桨，击空明兮溯流光" target="_blank">Meaningless Nothingness</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://sizheng.org/" title="" target="_blank">夏小雪的星球散步</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://changingmoments.one/" title="" target="_blank">蝴蝶曾在此处</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://trails-of-isara.vercel.app/" title="把最棒的吊桥效应献给你" target="_blank">深海鱼拒绝触礁</a></li>
        <li class="hover:underline"><a href="https://sanguok.com" title="左海逐月，雙峰遺夢" target="_blank">山月</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>
</Layout>
